{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SpaceSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.paddingBlockMedium","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC31spacePaddingBlockDensityDefaultSdvp","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddingblockdensitydefault"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault":{"role":"symbol","title":"spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddingblockdensitydefault","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.paddingBlockMedium","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacePaddingBlockDensityDefault"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"title":"Theme Orange"}}}